George Bancroft (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/George_Bancroft_(actor) 0 George Bancroft (September 30, 1882 – October 2, 1956) was an American film actor, whose career spanned more than thirty years from 1925 to 1956. He was cast in many notable films alongside major film stars throughout his Hollywood years.
